1.For database testing below are the maven dependencies which needs to be added to the POM.

i. MySQL Dependency.
======================
<!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/mysql/mysql-connector-java -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>mysql</groupId>
    <artifactId>mysql-connector-java</artifactId>
    <version>8.0.15</version>
</dependency>



2.For database testing below are required information which will help in creating a communication channel.
 i.   driver for database (jdbc driver).
 ii.  url 
 iii. username
 iv.  password 
 
 

